  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short existential horror experience<br></li><li>Explore a vast star system<br></li><li>Complete tasks to keep your space ship in shape<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Several secrets<br></li><li>Survive whatever lurks in the void</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/92284707788d2845e59b1237f08e225b.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NAVIGATE</h2>Your mission is to <strong>navigate</strong> through a star system and <strong>scan</strong> various planets to find a habitable environment. It won't be that easy, as space is an unforgivable, dangerous void. <strong>Stay alive</strong> by avoiding dangers and repairing your spacecraft.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.poster.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.webm?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.mp4?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER</h2>Scan objects and anomalies floating in space to find remnants of what happened in this star system and clues to what happened to yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.poster.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.webm?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.mp4?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/95ba6f7ade649c9d7068fca8adb6ea04.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>Your home planet has been <strong>destroyed</strong> and there's no turning back. You're one of the lucky ones that has been sent out as a last resort to find another habitable planet and avoid extinction. The star system you've been assigned to explore may be subject to the same mysterious destruction yours was. Find out what happened and complete your mission.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short existential horror experience<br></li><li>Explore a vast star system<br></li><li>Complete tasks to keep your space ship in shape<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Several secrets<br></li><li>Survive whatever lurks in the void</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/92284707788d2845e59b1237f08e225b.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NAVIGATE</h2>Your mission is to <strong>navigate</strong> through a star system and <strong>scan</strong> various planets to find a habitable environment. It won't be that easy, as space is an unforgivable, dangerous void. <strong>Stay alive</strong> by avoiding dangers and repairing your spacecraft.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.poster.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.webm?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/75032cd89bd05e4f06382c987e28edea.mp4?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER</h2>Scan objects and anomalies floating in space to find remnants of what happened in this star system and clues to what happened to yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.poster.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.webm?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/ef3099bc21e7d41537dfabbcd512c6b5.mp4?t=1712440615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425500/extras/95ba6f7ade649c9d7068fca8adb6ea04.avif?t=1712440615\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>Your home planet has been <strong>destroyed</strong> and there's no turning back. You're one of the lucky ones that has been sent out as a last resort to find another habitable planet and avoid extinction. The star system you've been assigned to explore may be subject to the same mysterious destruction yours was. Find out what happened and complete your mission.",
